abstract: Fannie Mae reports net income of $1.3 billion for fourth quarter, down from $6.5 billion year earlier.
lead_paragraph: That figure is down sharply from $6.5 billion a year earlier, mostly because of losses on investments.

headline.main: Fannie Mae’s Quarterly Income Fell to $1.3. Billion
headline.print_headline: Fannie Mae’s Quarterly Income Fell to $1.3 Billion
